# Unit 4 Chapter 1 Project - Paper Prototype

Unit 4 Chapter 1 ends with students developing a paper prototype.  This is an opportunity for students to show how they considered the needs of others in solving a problem. This project also shows how students engaged in the Problem Solving Process.

